Name: task_assignment
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a task is assigned to a worker

Name: sprint_start_date
Description: The start date of a specific sprint

Name: feature_priority
Description: Numerical priority value assigned to a feature

Name: worker_utilization_rate
Description: The percentage of a worker's availability that is used

Name: story_point_allocation
Description: The number of story points assigned to a user story

Name: team_velocity_target
Description: The target velocity for a team in a specific sprint

Name: project_status
Description: The current status of a project (e.g.

Name: sprint_goal_achieved
Description: Binary variable: 1 if the sprint goal was achieved

Name: blocker_resolution_time
Description: The number of days taken to resolve a blocker

Name: skill_requirement_level
Description: The required proficiency level of a skill for a task
